            "content_kz": "<p>Qolda bar m&uacute;mkіndіkterge s&uacute;ıene otyryp, bіz arzan baǵamen avıabıletterdі al&yacute;ǵa k&oacute;mektes&yacute;ge, sondaı-aq shetelde jumys іste&yacute; &uacute;shіn jıі qajet bolatyn &oacute;mіrdі saqtandyr&yacute; m&aacute;selelerі boıynsha k&oacute;mek k&oacute;rset&yacute;ge daıynbyz</p>",
